---
layout: l_page
title: Brooklyn
---

// Partial download header for mobile and tablet viewport
= partial "partials/download-header-palm"

%header.page--header
    %a.page--header__link{:href => "../pages/nyc.html"} 
        .page--header__inner
            .page--book-half__container
                .page--book-half
                    .page--book-half__inner
                        .page--book-half__title My Favorite NYC
                        .page--book-half__bookcover{:style => "background-image: url(../images/about/ny.jpeg);"}
            .page--header--owner
                .page--header--owner__title
                    Owner
                .page--header--owner__name
                    Shota Setoguchi


%section.page--container


    // Partial download header for mobile and tablet viewport
    = partial "partials/download-header-lap"



    .page--inner
        .page--photo
            .page--photo--book-invisible
                %a.page--photo--book-invisible__inner{:href => "../pages/nyc.html"} 
                    .page--photo--book-invisible__container
                        .page--book-half__container
                            .page--book-half
                                .page--book-half__inner
                                    .page--book-half__title My Favorite NYC
                                    .page--book-half__bookcover{:style => "background-image: url(../images/about/ny.jpeg);"}
                        .page--header--owner
                            .page--header--owner__title
                                Owner
                            .page--header--owner__name
                                Shota Setoguchi
            
            .page--photo__howwasit.js-page--photo__howwasit
                .page--photo__num -45
                .page--photo__feeling.feeling__good bad!

            .img--holder
                %img{:src => "../images/placeholder/loader_page.gif", "data-src" => "../images/about/brooklyn.jpeg", :alt => "Brooklyn"}/ 


        .page--body
            %h1.page__title 
                BROOKLYN BRIDGE ブルックリン・ブリッジ
            %p.page__paragraph
                ブルックリン橋は20分ほどで渡ることができます。ブルックリン側はHigh st駅から。夕焼けにあわせて歩きはじめることをおすすめします！

                In this example the ‘border’ around the image is purely presentational, but I left it in there to show the inset effect off better. You can take it further by adding a 1px box-shadow or border to the bottom of the image with a colour lighter than the border, to give the effect of light shining off the inset edge (same as that popular technique to make text seem inset). 
                http://www.nycgo.com/
            .page--author
                %a.page--author__icon{:href => "../pages/nao.html"} 
                    %img.js-load{:src => "../images/usericon/shota.jpg", :alt => "Shota Setoguchi"}/ 
                .page--author__info
                    %span.page--author__title
                        Written by
                    %a.page--author__name{:href => "../pages/nao.html"} 
                        Shota Setoguchi

        
        // Partial share buttons
        = partial "partials/share-buttons"


    %nav.page--nav
        .page--nav__inner
            .page--read-next
                Read next

            %a.page--next{:href => "../pages/tomato.html"}
                .page--nav--link__lap
                    Tomato

        // Start footer from here
        = partial "partials/footer"
